Input.text_0: I love NY nails! John and Lanie are incredible! Their customer service is top notch, they're very hospitable. Call ahead to schedule an appointment. John shapes and styles your nails and they are to die for. I get compliments all the time! I've been a loyal customer since 2011.
Input.text_1:
Happy to recommend this restaurant!
Happy hour gives you some great options Spicy tuna roll,Salmon avocado roll , and the shrimp Tempura rolls were all fresh. The miso soup is good . If you like Sake they have a good selection.
A healthy choice while staying at the golden nugget!
We caught the happy hour everyday we stayed in Vegas
Input.text_2: This is one of my favorite places in Kensington. The Savory crepes are to die for. This place is good to go in the summer or winter. Even though the water kind of tastes weird, I would recommend this place.
Input.text_3: Wow! What a difference a few months makes! The new(ish) staff are amazingly attentive, knowledgeable, and helpful. Krispin and Nelson went out of their way to find me juice and a device that fit my needs and I will definitely be giving them my business from now on. They're funny guys too. Great move Kings of Vapor!
Input.text_4: Inka Heritage did a wonderful job with my book release party. The space looked good, the food was tasty and plentiful, the staff was friendly, and the owners even cut me a deal on our agreed-upon price after their success in drinks and new potential customers. I wish Daniel, Esmeralda and their staff continued success.
Input.text_5: I'm in town visiting my sister and we have been hanging out at her apartment. I love the property and the pool is awesome here. If I ever moved to Vegas, I would definitely check this place out. She has nothing but good things to say as well.
Input.text_6: This place gigantic. Prepare to spend some time walking around the massive space like I did, if you have no idea what you are looking for. They have everything you could imagine, and accessories galore. The staff are always friendly and very knowledgable. Pricing is really competitive too.
Input.text_7: These guys are amazing. My daughter was beyond nervous and they were so wonderful with her. They answered all her questions and explained everything to her before they did it. They are also fully equipped with lots of distractions including movies, games and over-the-top decor. Thank you for such a wonderful experience.
Input.text_8: Pittsburgh areas best wings! They broil them, not deep fried. Great flavor choices. Fries are fresh potatoes but a little greasy. Smell of cigars on occasion? Sometimes after work there are a couple of old guys puffing right beside the door. Decent selection of bottled beer.
Input.text_9: One of the best consumer experiences I've had in some time. Andy did a great job fitting me and explaining everything. Lots of choice for sure but the sheer competence of Andy showed through. I highly recommend weather you're a seasoned runner or an all-too-occasional walker/exerciser like me! Nice job, Andy!
